        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer939740390" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14026253989280615462">I find it hard to review this book - since it was written so many years ago, and that this translation was written so many year go by Mary Anne Evans under the George Eliot guise doesn&apos;t make it any easier. Therefore, I wont&apos;t assign any stars - not that it&apos;s a horrible book, I&apos;m just reading it out of its own time and context. That&apos;s why.<br/><br/>Nevertheless, it&apos;s an important book which changed the way we think about Christianity and religion in general and for that reason alone I found it worth readi</span>
  <span id="freeText14026253989280615462" style="display:none">I find it hard to review this book - since it was written so many years ago, and that this translation was written so many year go by Mary Anne Evans under the George Eliot guise doesn't make it any easier. Therefore, I wont't assign any stars - not that it's a horrible book, I'm just reading it out of its own time and context. That's why.<br /><br />Nevertheless, it's an important book which changed the way we think about Christianity and religion in general and for that reason alone I found it worth reading.<br /><br />At times I lost focus, either because of the old English language or the other people being namedropped here, which made no bells rang what so ever.<br /><br />If you want to read this important document first hand, do it. But you might be just as happy reading <i>about</i> it and its author.<br /><br />That said, I'm glad I pulled through and finished.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14026253989280615462" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
