<li class='cover' id='bookCover_2638701'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2638701-violence"><img alt="Violence: Six Sideways Reflections" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1344316147l/2638701._SX98_.jpg" />
